    "body": "@onbjerg I think we need to make `has_missing_dependencies` a bit smarter:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/commit/54191b6aada33a8a7c3593d135caa8179f167855#diff-584cf95bca62c6fe76e213c6d050986d08a053a64fb8363ebd0dabf53ebab0afR151\r\n\r\nrn it only checks submodule status, but there could be any kind of submodule.\r\n\r\n`-6458fb2780a3092bc756e737f246be1de6d3d362 lib/solidity-bytes-utils`\r\n\r\nit should check that `lib/solidity-bytes-utils` is in lib folder\r\n\r\nalso should bypass this if git is not available I think\r\n",
